[b]TESTERS[/b] - None needed A.T.M.
This is how the organization will be. Once we get a forum set up, we will have the coders of the server make tutorials, please post them in the form of a poll. If they get enough votes for yes, then they get added to the server. The same will go for client sided tutorials, this project is NOT reccomended for nooby coders and I do reserve the right to decline any person(s) of whom I see unfit to code this server. This server is NOT going to be made from a pimpscape source, it's going to be made from an older, more stable source. There will be less lag and shit than the older models.
Any member loyal to this cause will get a client, and a copy of the source. NOBODY who immidiately joins will ask for a copy of either, they will not be given away until your worthiness has been proven to me, or other members of high status.
I am currently working on getting Project Null copyrighted.
Any body who so wished to get me an FTP and a free domain name may do so, I will allow you to run the entire forum that will be made. And your rule there will be law, not mine.
Please apply using this format:
[code][b]Position name:[/b] [i]the name of the position you want[/i] [b]My Work[/b]: [i]post some links to your work and anything else you wish for me to see[/i] [b]Pick-Me[/b]: [i]Explain, in-depth, why I should pick you, please use proper english.[/i] [b]MSN/AIM[/b]: [i]Let me contact you, give me your msn or aim[/i][/code]
I hope you decide to apply.
